### Windows Users

Please append `.bat` to any of the provided ruby-based binaries

eg.

```ps1
  .\pact\bin\pact-broker.bat
```

Please append `.exe` to any of the provided rust based binaries

eg.

```ps1
  .\pact\bin\pact_mock_server_cli.exe
```

